Standard Bank to Take Deposits at Spaza Shops, Mail Says

-- B y   J a n a   M a r a i s
-- 
2011-09-07T12:05:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/standard-bank-to-take-deposits-at-spaza-shops-mail-says.html
Standard Bank  Group Ltd. will start
taking deposits from clients at spaza shops, informal
 convenience stores  often run from home, in October, Financial
Mail said.  The bank will also roll out ATMs and other electronic
banking channels at its 8,000 bank shops, the Johannesburg-based
Financial Mail quoted Herman Singh, chief executive officer of
Beyond Payments, a unit of Standard Bank, as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jana Marais in Johannesburg at 
 jmarais@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  